== Usage ==
;name:Name of the tool
;image:An image illustrating the item 
;caption:Caption for the image above
;other_name:Other name(s) used for this item
;classification:General type, e.g. hand tool, power tool, garden tool, etc.
;uses:What is this item used for, e.g. cutting, concentrating force, guiding, protecting, seizing and holding, etc.
;types:Different types of this tool, e.g. hammer = ball-peen hammer, cross-peen hammer, etc.
;used_with:Tools that this one is used in conjunction with, e.g. hammer + chisel, punc, etc.
;inventor:Inventor(s) of the item (if any)
;manufacturer:If this is an item specific to a particular manufacturer, put the name here
;model:if this is a particular manufacturer's model, put the model name or number here
;related:related tools, e.g. hammer = axe, maul, etc.

